-- Resolving Australia's Mine Tax Dispute a Priority for Gillard, Crean Says
-- Marion Rae
-- 2010-06-28T21:58:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/resolving-australia-s-mine-tax-dispute-a-priority-for-gillard-crean-says.html

          
          
             Australian Prime Minister Julia
Gillard made it clear resolving the dispute with industry over
the proposed mining tax is a priority and goodwill exists on
both sides, Employment Minister Simon Crean told Australian
Broadcasting Corp. radio today.  
